    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/7c82745b3a9544aa49701eead19ebfdf.poster.avif?t=1772209514\" width=960 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/7c82745b3a9544aa49701eead19ebfdf.webm?t=1772209514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>你将探索遥远反乌托邦未来的废墟，在这个需要应对高强度快节奏战斗的残酷世界中生存下来。掌握数十种连招，在敌群中掀起腥风血雨。<br>我们以坚韧和激情打出这款快节奏的轻度肉鸽游戏，让你得以在战斗中实时变形切换角色，通过技能组合拉风地击溃对手。<br>通过关卡，强化实力，解锁强劲升级通道。<br>但一旦死亡……所有努力尽付东流……直到你重振旗鼓再度出发。<br><br>一开始，《Morbid Metal》只是一个大学单人副业企划，最终它蜕变为完整的团队之作。这是 SCREEN JUICE 的首部作品，该独立工作室由原项目创始人成立。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/9f3a3e4d3337df6a107d24ea55e1496b.poster.avif?t=1772209514\" width=960 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/9f3a3e4d3337df6a107d24ea55e1496b.webm?t=1772209514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在这款轻肉鸽游戏中，生存之道在于实时切换角色，正如 FPS 中实时切换武器一般。<br>你队伍中的每位成员都有各自的专属动作组和标志性特殊技能。将共计衔接成独特的连招，你的所过之处将只剩腥风血雨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/e3d9b06e3c28a44550f6929b7e7b1631.poster.avif?t=1772209514\" width=960 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/e3d9b06e3c28a44550f6929b7e7b1631.webm?t=1772209514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>每一轮游戏，你都可以升级自己的角色，逐步变强，直至碾压对手。你将在战斗中进化，收集例程，解锁协议增益效果，消耗神经片段强化实力。而死亡会重置轮回。不过我们的永久升级系统会确保每一轮游戏都别具一格。你会死亡、适应，随后进化。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/7ab92d65b523c46574492a9fef1ae6c3.poster.avif?t=1772209514\" width=960 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/7ab92d65b523c46574492a9fef1ae6c3.webm?t=1772209514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>你将在崩溃后的模拟世界中，化身为神秘主控制造的最终 AI。你的使命：清除腐化的同类，超越人类。每次循环都会揭示一点点被遗忘的真相。通过惊艳的高保真画质，你将见证人类自我毁灭的全程。<br>战斗、死亡、重生……直到你领悟自己的本质。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/75bda006c3c4df6aa5947a437e27ad3c.poster.avif?t=1772209514\" width=960 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866130/extras/75bda006c3c4df6aa5947a437e27ad3c.webm?t=1772209514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
